Seto, a studious but unremarkable student, constantly finds himself in provocative situations with Anjo, the popular girl in his class who can't seem to stop teasing him. A heart-pounding teen rom-com bursting with youthful passion! (Source: Emaqi) Note: This is a serialisation of the web comic originally self-published on Pixiv.
